          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1757.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a medium heat</p><p>Tip: Add a drizzle of oil if your pan is looking a little dry!</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced carrot </strong>and<strong> chopped</strong> <strong>onion </strong>with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> to the pan and cook for 5 min or until they begin to soften</p><p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1757.-step-4-x200.jpg",
