    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>spaghetti</strong> to a pot of<strong> boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>spaghetti </strong>for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the<strong> spaghetti</strong> and return it to the pot</p>",
